WEBVTT

00:00:00.867 --> 00:00:04.539
So, raise your hand
if you've seen somebody in your city

00:00:04.563 --> 00:00:07.942
standing on a corner,
holding a sign like this.

00:00:10.409 --> 00:00:11.658
I think we all have.

00:00:11.682 --> 00:00:12.847
If you're being honest,

00:00:12.871 --> 00:00:15.488
at least one time,
have you wondered if they mean it?

00:00:16.758 --> 00:00:19.665
If we offered them a job,
would they really take it?

00:00:19.689 --> 00:00:22.170
And what would that job mean
to them in their lives?

00:00:23.243 --> 00:00:26.044
Well, this is a story
about what happened in my city

00:00:26.068 --> 00:00:27.620
when we decided to find out,

00:00:28.712 --> 00:00:32.099
when we decided to think differently
about panhandling,